  %img{style: 'width: 40px;', src: "/youtube.png"}
%h2 Categor√≠as
- uniq_categories.each do |name|
  - if controller.controller_name == 'posts'
    = link_to name, tag_path(name), class: "#{contains_category_name(post, name) ? 'label-category' : 'label-normal' }"
  - else
    = link_to name, tag_path(name), class: 'label-category'
%h2 Tags
- uniq_tags.each do |name|
  - if controller.controller_name == 'posts'
    = link_to name, tag_path(name), class: "#{contains_tag_name(post, name) ? 'label-tag' : 'label-normal'}"
  - else
    = link_to name, tag_path(name), class: 'label-tag'